      "text": "Seikima II Akuma no Gyakushū! (聖飢魔II 悪魔の逆襲！; lit. \"Seikima II The Wrath of Satan!\") is a video game that was released in Japan in 1986.\nIn 1987, the game was re-released for the MSX2 under the title Seikima II Special (聖飢魔IIスペシャル) with more detailed sprites and backgrounds. It also featured actual Seikima-II music.",
